@startuml
title C4 Container – US 2.2.5 Organizations

actor "Port Authority\nOfficer" as Officer

node "Client Layer" {
  [UI / API Client] as Client
}

node "Web API" {
  [OrganizationsController] as Ctl
}

node "Application Layer" {
  [OrganizationService] as Svc
}

database "Persistence" as Db
node "Domain" as Dom {
  [Organization] as Org
  [Representative] as Rep
}

Officer --> Client : register organizations
Client --> Ctl : POST/GET
Ctl --> Svc : CRUD operations
Svc --> Db : persist/retrieve
Svc ..> Org : create
Org *-- Rep : ≥1 representative

note right of Org
  Organization:
  - Unique ID
  - Legal name (required)
  - Alternative name (optional)
  - Address
  - Tax number (unique)
  - ≥1 Representative
end note

note right of Rep
  Representative:
  - Name
  - Citizen ID
  - Nationality (ISO 3166-1)
  - Email (unique globally)
  - Phone (optional)
end note

@enduml
